document.title: WFT
document.intro: Wurdboek fan de Fryske taal (Wft) online is the electronic version of the WFT: a historical and scientific dictionary of the Dutch language. The dictionary decribes the meaning and history of hundred thousands of words in written Frisian, from the period 1800-1976. Modern Dutch Lemma and Frisian lemma Describes the origin of a word describes the meaning of a words describes the structure of a word
